name: FirstLineAntibioticsForCommonChildhoodInfections
title: First Line Antibiotics for Common Childhood Infections
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set collects RxNorm codes for antibiotics recommended as first-line treatment for common childhood infections in children without allergy to these drugs.),(Data Element Scope: Both drug form and formulation codes drawn from RxNorm based on SCDFs for recommended antibiotics, with additional curation.),(Inclusion Criteria: RxNorm codes subsumed by clinical drug forms comprised by SCDFs for first-line antibiotics),(Exclusion Criteria: SCDFs with names indicating intended topical use)
